scopecontent.p:
This collection includes minutes of annual meetings (1981-1996), the executive
                    committee, and board of directors; subject and correspondence files; budget,
                    audit, and other financial records; covenant agreements; APCU Risk Management;
                    Business Education Initiative records, 1994-2001; Point of View newsletters and
                    related records, 1990-2002; constitution and by-laws; committee minutes;
                    membership fact sheets and membership votes; newsletters; memoranda; reports;
                    and guidelines, 1976-1981. Also included are the files of Duncan Ferguson,
                    President of APCU.
